---------------------------
AV MIXER INSTALLATION GUIDE
---------------------------

Dependencies
============

FFMPEG 1.2 with libx264
OpenCV 2.4.6.1
Live555
Media Streamer (https://github.com/ua-i2cat/media-streamer)

Installation
============

git clone https://github.com/ua-i2cat/mixer.git
cd mixer
./autogen --prefix=installation_path --enable-stats
make
make install

NOTE: default prefix is /usr/local
NOTE: enable-stats flag in order to enable statistics management and display. Disabled by default.

Usage
=====

controller management_port (p.e. controller 7777)

NOTE: listening port for incoming streams is by default 5004.


